snippet.title: FAR CRY® NEW DAWN – Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Chaos. Pain. Mayhem.
Are you ready to fight for survival in this post apocalyptic frontier?

Far Cry® New Dawn will be available on PS4, Xbox One and PC on February 15th, 2019

More info: www.farcrygame.com
